id=vrshell_zygisk
name=VrShell AIO (Zygisk inject)
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=xAstroBoy
description=Injects the VrShell AIO patches (moonjump / far-clip / teleport / player-ctl / on-device dumper) into com.oculus.vrshell via Zygisk. Stock VrShell.apk is untouched (no repack, no mount, no re-sign) so the platform signature + horizonos perms stay intact.
